      <p class="lead">SplitDodgeTours has created a lacrosse based immersion experience centered around a professional lacrosse game.</p><p>  Tours travel by the <%= link_to "lacrosse fun bus", bus_path, class: 'link_outline', rel: 'canonical'  %> to Denver from SLC. On the trip to and from riders are treated to games, lacrosse gear giveaways, videos and demonstrations.</p>

