      <p>Questions? Please <%= link_to "get in touch", contact_path, class: 'link_outline', rel: 'canonical' %>or you can find out more about who's behind the tour <%= link_to "here", about_path, class: 'link_outline', rel: 'canonical' %>.</p> 
